From 4830f824348e07f252dc8d22a195c6f51b2ca180 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Thu, 18 Jun 2026 21:18:06 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix(fve): use hibs fixtures API for lines collector instead
 of watchlist

--from-watchlist imports scrapers.fotmob_client which is not available in
the FVE Docker worker image, causing ModuleNotFoundError on every repair
and cron tick.

Add run_fve_lines_collector.sh to pull fixture keys from /api/fve/fixtures
and run the collector with --fixtures via docker compose exec.
---
